<p>Hello and welcome to my author page! I first discovered the Foundation in late 2016, and have been a huge fan ever since. Since you're here, feel free to check out my body of work. I hope you enjoy!</p>
<p>I'm also a wiki Moderator attached to the Forum Criticism team (and the Wikiwalk team too (and the Rewrite team as well(Also the Internet Outreach team))). If you ever want a draft critiqued, just shoot me a message. I serve as the team captain for Rewrite and Co-Captain for Internet Outreach, so contact me if you have any questions about those processes.</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/modern_erasmus?alert=2">If you like my work please support me on Patreon!</a></strong></p>
